This test is based on the Mockito Tutorial by tutorialspoint.com:
https://www.tutorialspoint.com/mockito/index.htm

Note: This code uses mockito 2.10.0 which is based on Byte Buddy. To
switch to the old cglib-based mockito, use the 2.0.2-beta dependency
in build.gradle.

To analyze this project, 'gradle analyze' is not enough, as Soot may
miss some classes. You should use the "fat JAR" provided and post it
via gradle-plugin:

  (without HPROF information)
  build-tools% ./gradlew :gradle-plugin:replayPost -Pargs="full-path-to/fat-doop-project/"

  (with HPROF information)
  build-tools% ./gradlew :gradle-plugin:replayPost -Pargs="full-path-to/fat-doop-project-hprof/"
